b:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Feature Analysis"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"Both Crello and Looka share a solid foundation of core features including Templates, Drag And Drop, Brand Kit, Export Formats. Where Crello pulls ahead is with exclusive access to Collaboration and Animations and Stock Assets, which can be a deciding factor for teams that rely on these capabilities. On the other hand, Looka uniquely offers Ai Generation, giving it an edge for users who prioritize this area. \n\nLooking at user ratings, Crello holds an overall score of 6/10 and an ease of use score of 7/10, while Looka scores 7/10 overall and 9/10 for ease of use. These ratings reflect real user experiences and can indicate differences in usability, support quality, and overall satisfaction."}]]}]
c:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Pricing Breakdown"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"When it comes to pricing, Crello offers a more budget-friendly entry point at Free, compared to Looka's starting price of $20 one-time. Crello has a notable advantage here with its free plan, allowing you to get started without any financial commitment. Looka does not currently offer a free tier, which means you will need to pay from day one."}]]}]
